text:
The Ukrainian authorities give success to the workers for their own sake instead of taking real steps
01 Nov 2019, 16:45 by Maxim Goldarb

In 2018, workers transferred almost $ 11 billion to Ukraine. 12 billion (10% of GDP) are expected this year. The "green" government reports with the help of labor money about the "successes" and "growth" of the economy.

Maxim Goldarb wrote about it on his Facebook page.
Instead of using all possible means, such as:

tax cuts for domestic businesses;
its targeted cheap lending to domestic banks;
protection of the domestic producer against the expansion of imports;
credit and tax grace periods when starting your business;
a complete ban on law enforcement agencies' interference in business activities;
reviewing EU quotas to balance imports and exports and equal opportunities for our entrepreneurs;
increase of social payments and indexation for the return of people's lost solvency for Poroshenko, which will cause a spike in consumption in the domestic market;

The authorities don't do or even try anything like this, but simply state the digital facts and draw unnecessary graphs. Ukrainians continue to leave, Ukraine is aging and depopulated, becoming a convenient, clearing place for the expansion of foreign technological capital from the unnecessary population.
So in the 21st century, with specially created conditions, with the assistance of local authorities, not war, the territories and national riches of our state are captured.

Maxim Goldarb


